    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a><h1 id="栈的应用（stack）"><a href="#栈的应用（stack）" class="headerlink" title="栈的应用（stack）"></a>栈的应用（stack）</h1><h2 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><p>栈（stack）是一种<strong>后进先出</strong>的数据结构，栈顶指针始终指向栈最上方元素，栈空时令 <code>TOP=-1</code></p><h2 id="常用操作"><a href="#常用操作" class="headerlink" title="常用操作"></a>常用操作</h2><p>数组 <code>st[]</code> 来实现栈，int 型变量 <code>TOP</code> 表示栈顶元素下标（下标从 0 开始），栈空时 TOP = -1 </p><h3 id="清空（clear）"><a href="#清空（clear）" class="headerlink" title="清空（clear）"></a>清空（clear）</h3><p>将栈顶指针 TOP 置为 -1</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">clear</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    TOP = <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="获取栈内元素个数（size）"><a href="#获取栈内元素个数（size）" class="headerlink" title="获取栈内元素个数（size）"></a>获取栈内元素个数（size）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">size</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> TOP + <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="判空（empty）"><a href="#判空（empty）" class="headerlink" title="判空（empty）"></a>判空（empty）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">empty</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(TOP == <span class="number">-1</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="进栈（push）"><a href="#进栈（push）" class="headerlink" title="进栈（push）"></a>进栈（push）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">push</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    st[++TOP] = x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="出栈（pop）"><a href="#出栈（pop）" class="headerlink" title="出栈（pop）"></a>出栈（pop）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">pop</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    TOP--;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="取栈顶元素（top）"><a href="#取栈顶元素（top）" class="headerlink" title="取栈顶元素（top）"></a>取栈顶元素（top）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">top</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> st[TOP];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用<code>pop()</code>和<code>top()</code>之前必须先使用<code>empty()</code>判断栈是否为空</p><h1 id="队列的应用（queue）"><a href="#队列的应用（queue）" class="headerlink" title="队列的应用（queue）"></a>队列的应用（queue）</h1><h2 id="基本概念-1"><a href="#基本概念-1" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h2><p>队列（queue）是一种<strong>先进先出</strong>的数据结构，队首指针 front 指向<strong>队首元素的前一个位置</strong>，队尾指针 rear 指向<strong>队尾元素</strong>，初始状态 <code>front = -1</code>、<code>rear = -1</code></p><h2 id="常用操作-1"><a href="#常用操作-1" class="headerlink" title="常用操作"></a>常用操作</h2><p>数组 <code>q[]</code> 实现队列，队列为空时，int型变量 front = -1、rear = -1</p><h3 id="清空（clear）-1"><a href="#清空（clear）-1" class="headerlink" title="清空（clear）"></a>清空（clear）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">clear</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    front = rear = <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="获取队列内元素个数（size）"><a href="#获取队列内元素个数（size）" class="headerlink" title="获取队列内元素个数（size）"></a>获取队列内元素个数（size）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">size</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> rear - front;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="判空（empty）-1"><a href="#判空（empty）-1" class="headerlink" title="判空（empty）"></a>判空（empty）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">empty</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">if</span>(front == rear) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="入队（push）"><a href="#入队（push）" class="headerlink" title="入队（push）"></a>入队（push）</h3><p>队尾指针 rear 指向队尾元素，元素入队时，先把 rear + 1 ，然后再存放到 rear 指向的位置</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">push</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    q[++rear] = x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="出队（pop"><a href="#出队（pop" class="headerlink" title="出队（pop)"></a>出队（pop)</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">pop</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    front++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="取队首元素（get-front"><a href="#取队首元素（get-front" class="headerlink" title="取队首元素（get_front)"></a>取队首元素（get_front)</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">get_front</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> q[front + <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="取队尾元素（get-rear）"><a href="#取队尾元素（get-rear）" class="headerlink" title="取队尾元素（get_rear）"></a>取队尾元素（get_rear）</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">get_rear</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> q[rear];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
